_sText:
Hi Guys, this is my first Map, made with a friend (x<X^) for the Wiremod.ru Mapping Competition (Now Serverscape.net)
There are 3 Areas with ca. 6 Traps per Area and some secret grenades/places and an secret End)


Some more facts:
Traps: 17 (Counted only the Traps which can be triggered by Killer/Terrorist)

Spawnpoints: (Runner/CT): 90
(Killer/Terrorist): 5
1x: info_player_start (For Singleplayer testing)

3d-Skybox: Yes

Secrets: 6 (1 Medicgrenade, 1 Smokegrenade, 1 Flashbang, Secret Ghostroom, another Secret grenade and the Secret End (with Grenades :D)

Endings: Bhop
Old
Knife
Secret-Grenade End

Environment: Inside, like a tube
